Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.80,0:00:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能看見痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.28,0:00:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是空虛地渡過每一日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.52,0:00:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在充滿消沉心情的城市裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.96,0:00:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你在優美地閃耀着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.03,0:00:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't Stop！\NCarry On！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.86,0:00:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要灰心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.33,0:00:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't Stop！\NShinin Oh！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.24,0:00:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要被破壞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.27,0:00:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成愛啊，\N像把宇宙包裏一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.98,0:01:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在抱緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.32,0:01:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在抱緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.44,0:01:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索的爸爸，漢格魯.艾賓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.08,0:01:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身在成為神聖軍事同盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.65,0:01:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新旗艦的珍路.達古上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.02,0:01:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索告訴了爸爸媽媽的死訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.49,0:01:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也因為爸爸變了而動搖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.99,0:01:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但在比列騰的\N宇宙艦隊攻過來時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.47,0:01:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索在爸爸面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.63,0:01:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顯示自己成長後的姿態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.04,0:01:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想吸引他的注意力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.94,0:02:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鮮血在光的漩渦裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.28,0:02:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想用防護罩消滅我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.82,0:02:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人救了我！ 是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.06,0:02:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是奧迪羅和湯馬殊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.13,0:02:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們一直在保護着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.23,0:02:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.30,0:02:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，我幫到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.84,0:02:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.64,0:02:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為世伯看着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.24,0:02:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你太起勁了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.21,0:02:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太起勁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.75,0:02:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有因此而情緒高漲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.35,0:02:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為機師，\N如果我不落力戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.78,0:02:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會被爸爸責備的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.23,0:02:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是很棘手的艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.93,0:02:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一防衛線被衝破了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.40,0:02:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達斯羅上校的 [舒百騰]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.24,0:03:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來無動靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.50,0:03:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.00,0:03:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們集結在本艦\N後方4千米附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.21,0:03:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們要求支援前\N他不會行動嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.08,0:03:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們後退到第二防衛線！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.52,0:03:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人艦隊在後退！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.62,0:03:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪羅！ 湯馬殊！\N你們知道嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.23,0:03:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們無理由知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.86,0:03:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑斯柏也有不少的艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.90,0:03:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們集合的話就麻煩了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佈下了耀目的機雷！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.14,0:03:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.91,0:03:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻到這裡已夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.98,0:03:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後退吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.48,0:03:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在拉斯迪奧艦隊後方\N有其他艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.55,0:03:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那隊艦隊好像就是那部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在飛碟上的\N機動戰士駐守的部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.15,0:03:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在飛碟上的大型機動戰士！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.59,0:03:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是\N那部機動戰士發出鈴聲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.99,0:04:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且，在那隊艦隊後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有那個叫凱羅天使的環啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.03,0:04:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，首先出戰的艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.00,0:04:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立即就後退，為甚麽呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.94,0:04:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我方數目眾多，他們害怕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.71,0:04:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麽，之後就更辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.51,0:04:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從凱羅天使\N也會有艦隊出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.08,0:04:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像從那裡也聼到鈴聲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，卡魯曼很寧靜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.89,0:04:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些鈴聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.59,0:04:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像和在地球聼到的不同呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.16,0:04:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像要令人害怕和引誘別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直聼到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.57,0:04:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和聼到有點不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.37,0:04:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在腦内感到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.81,0:04:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們除了看到\N那部飛碟型傢伙時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.34,0:04:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們聼不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.65,0:05:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比列騰司令在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.59,0:05:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無理由知道吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.29,0:05:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即是在他自己的房裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.66,0:05:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做甚麽！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.63,0:05:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從我險些\N被斷頭台分屍以來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.30,0:05:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好怕那種聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.73,0:05:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.07,0:05:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也沒告訴你凱羅天使的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.94,0:05:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對卡格持的\N做法存有疑問吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.17,0:05:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，但你只是叫我去前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.01,0:05:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在停戰協定簽定後，\N你和格諾古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.35,0:05:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被調離地球淨化作戰\N而回到宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.55,0:05:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只顧自己啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.72,0:05:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個古怪的女人是誰！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是和你打招呼呢，上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是露比.施羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.83,0:05:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是下次作戰前的\N休息時間呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.93,0:05:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即是說我得不到支援嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.53,0:05:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒那樣說！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.60,0:05:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我剛才所說一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.24,0:05:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要固\N凱羅天使的防衛陣勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.21,0:05:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,始終只是把我們做擋箭牌！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.58,0:05:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露比.施羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.35,0:05:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是穿在機師服上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.61,0:06:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何不妥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.05,0:06:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…  你不討厭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要看時間和場合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.82,0:06:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達斯羅和卡格持是合謀的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.36,0:06:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那次斷頭台行刑是做戲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.86,0:06:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是為了不讓贊斯卡羅的國民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.53,0:06:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我們莫托拉度艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.33,0:06:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道這個凱羅天使的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聼聞凱羅天使完成後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.40,0:06:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會成為巨大的腦波發訊裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.20,0:06:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然他們想用這東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.91,0:06:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以精神控制人類的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.91,0:06:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就要由我們來使用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.41,0:06:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連卡格持等人也要控制嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫艦長來商量作戰計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.58,0:06:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.37,0:06:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校，我聼到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.74,0:06:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但讓比列騰指揮沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.64,0:06:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個機師能有甚麽作為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.14,0:07:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他為了諷刺我\N而努力作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.04,0:07:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就能替我消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.01,0:07:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神聖軍事同盟的艦隊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.75,0:07:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，\N之後我就去消滅比列騰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.65,0:07:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們面向聯邦軍的進攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.72,0:07:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後退到舒百騰艦隊的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.26,0:07:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣，達斯羅也要行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.43,0:07:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那部贊歷古會出戰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.13,0:07:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那由我從後面消滅它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.07,0:07:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時如果能把\N白色傢伙牽連在内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.10,0:07:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就很有趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.81,0:07:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大命的達斯羅也會被消滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.65,0:07:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你穿上\N一套我喜歡的新衫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.05,0:07:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能那樣說的資格…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.32,0:07:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男女交往的資格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打勝仗讓我看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.39,0:07:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和年輕的男仔接吻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.56,0:07:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令男人認真也很花工夫！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.10,0:08:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來已完成了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.34,0:08:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是比列騰自己用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.64,0:08:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥司令用機動堡壘，\N比基拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.65,0:08:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來能使用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是身為機師會很輕鬆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝上飛彈盒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.53,0:08:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想照自己意思戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.53,0:08:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去衡量人類的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.27,0:08:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新類型人的話會明白我呢，\N細路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.67,0:08:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在敵人宇宙艦隊會合前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要消滅\N敵人的第一道防線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.41,0:08:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士出發後，全艦追擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.81,0:08:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要被自己人的砲彈擊中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.95,0:08:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒勒隊一號機，HEXA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌莉.費殊，出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.19,0:08:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二號機，HEXA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.76,0:08:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美愛娜.格特，出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.46,0:09:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新型雷射盾？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.63,0:09:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在做甚麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.40,0:09:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在調整馬力機能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.74,0:09:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能使用吧 無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.14,0:09:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要小心\N不要被它的力量連累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.71,0:09:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道，我試試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.74,0:09:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒勒隊五號機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭謝茜嘉.哈拿，出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.45,0:09:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然今次由\N聯邦軍的主力去前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.56,0:09:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那部飛碟型機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不由我們應付的話\N應該不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.03,0:09:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.53,0:09:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索說要試試米加雷射砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.90,0:09:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過或許會\N交給由加小姐你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.87,0:09:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交給我也沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.74,0:09:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以因為V2威力強大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.41,0:09:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就獨自戰鬥啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.58,0:09:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，哈羅也在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.05,0:09:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V2，出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.58,0:09:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要心急，知道嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.92,0:10:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以被鈴聲引過去啊，\N胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.99,0:10:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.26,0:10:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為爸爸正在\N看着我怎樣戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑斯柏也很頑強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.67,0:10:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，佔上風的是我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.31,0:10:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.95,0:10:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能接近拉斯迪奧！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.88,0:10:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.22,0:10:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是胡索救了我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要利用車胎嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.86,0:10:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我假裝追着他的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就能混入敵人當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.77,0:10:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有差勁的敵人追來，胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.47,0:10:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是湯馬殊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.74,0:10:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能繼續接近\N莫托拉度艦隊就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.54,0:10:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鈴聲！ ？在哪裡！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.02,0:11:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是從正面的莫托拉度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.12,0:11:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯迪奧艦隊傳來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.45,0:11:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是從更後面來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.26,0:11:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱羅天使！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.26,0:11:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是\N湯馬殊、奧迪羅和由加小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.85,0:11:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪貝德小姐，\N果然是這個方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.88,0:11:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.49,0:11:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們去下面的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.19,0:11:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡魯曼再有反常的話，\N你通知我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.49,0:11:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.26,0:11:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖，我知道你害怕鈴聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.59,0:11:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會寧靜的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.30,0:11:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.57,0:11:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,華倫，用飛彈掩護 知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.57,0:11:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.14,0:12:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡魯曼，飲奶就沒事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.38,0:12:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就會聼不到鈴聲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.78,0:12:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.32,0:12:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要趁現在固定身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.39,0:12:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.16,0:12:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭達斯也想要媽媽嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.49,0:12:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今次是二時的方向，姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.70,0:12:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.17,0:12:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪貝德小姐，正面迴避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.73,0:12:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡里路 知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.77,0:12:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利害！ 回到宇宙後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.97,0:12:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們的感覺變得很敏銳！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.37,0:12:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.91,0:12:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可能只是被吸引住啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.58,0:12:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被吸引住？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.31,0:12:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且，我覺得這樣有點溫暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.88,0:12:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在地球感到的溫暖感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.05,0:12:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐講得無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.92,0:12:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡魯曼時哭時笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.02,0:12:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不只是因為他害怕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.16,0:12:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索等人正在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.86,0:12:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能感到\N溫暖感覺的宇宙裡戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.33,0:12:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.43,0:12:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.47,0:13:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我知道那是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.84,0:13:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三部，來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.71,0:13:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…個盾的力量\N令我部機過熱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.92,0:13:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盾牌馬力強大\N就是指這回事嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.03,0:13:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主螢光幕被擊毀了！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.19,0:13:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,控制器也失靈嗎！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.70,0:13:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的爆炸是！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.24,0:13:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是舒勒隊的HEXA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.07,0:13:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰的機體？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.32,0:13:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得有新武器也不能運用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HEXA也是\N以V高達做基礎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.09,0:13:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是機體的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.26,0:14:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,始終是我無力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.60,0:14:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個細路就能運用嗎，胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.95,0:14:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麽？ 我不害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.29,0:14:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我感到那個胡索嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.69,0:14:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很美麗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.03,0:14:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還可支持一小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.68,0:14:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是白色方舟的奧迪羅嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.95,0:15:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是富蘭尼小姐吧，\N空氣沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.96,0:15:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.56,0:15:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒受傷吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.93,0:15:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先把這個盾交給V2！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.16,0:15:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是後面那個盾嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.20,0:15:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米加雷射盾的馬力很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.70,0:15:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HEXA不能使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.84,0:15:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.44,0:15:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擊沉一艘！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.88,0:15:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.91,0:15:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是敵人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.38,0:15:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了！ 細路！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.25,0:15:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要報被你咬我胸部的仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.20,0:15:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.77,0:15:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把艾勒度的環割斷了嗎！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.80,0:15:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索！ 你沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米加雷射砲被擊毀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.14,0:15:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就這樣衝過去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.74,0:15:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌莉她們在前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.61,0:15:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.58,0:15:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一號艦中彈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.85,0:16:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它正離開戰線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.55,0:16:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.85,0:16:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.95,0:16:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒百騰艦隊\N也會被捲入戰鬥中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.15,0:16:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照預定一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.49,0:16:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們正逐漸進入戰鬥距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.26,0:16:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的指揮交給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.63,0:16:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要出擊嗎！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.36,0:16:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是坐在椅上戰鬥會完結嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要出擊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.04,0:16:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已進入敵艦\N砲擊的射程距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.04,0:16:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用出擊，比列騰還有力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.98,0:16:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不令他用盡力量會很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.55,0:16:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前進速度很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.79,0:16:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是令郎的功勞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.69,0:16:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，\N因為敵人前鋒拉斯迪奧艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.26,0:16:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正盡快和後方的艦隊會合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.10,0:16:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.04,0:16:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認同令郎的力量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.64,0:16:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.21,0:17:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.51,0:17:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着太利害的\N兒子是很痛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.41,0:17:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好像陌生人一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.41,0:17:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兒子超越父親這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.02,0:17:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想在面前看到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.79,0:17:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在後方艦隊後面的艦隊是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.06,0:17:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱羅天使呢，\N形狀已能看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.53,0:17:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎蒂，卡魯曼怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.83,0:17:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一直很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.97,0:17:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我好像也一直聼到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.24,0:17:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遠處的鈴聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.14,0:17:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.57,0:17:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附近有機動戰士嗎？\N沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索等人去了哪裡！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.49,0:17:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們由白色傢伙的左右進攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.89,0:17:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就由正面了結它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.26,0:17:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.90,0:18:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！ ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.34,0:18:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你中計了！ 細路！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.54,0:18:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！ ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我未輸的！ ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.11,0:18:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.39,0:18:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想讚你有點功夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.76,0:18:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你快睡在我的懷裡吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.56,0:18:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.43,0:18:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已逃不掉啊，細路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.87,0:18:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要得到我的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.40,0:18:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是露比小姐你的夢想！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.10,0:18:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，\N和拼命努力的細路在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.94,0:18:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的夢想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.84,0:18:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.15,0:18:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能反擊！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.98,0:18:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由加小姐！ 甚麽！ ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.35,0:18:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.62,0:18:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在我的懷裡\N成為我的所有吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.10,0:19:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能成為你的夢想！ ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.60,0:19:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是任何人的所有！ ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.77,0:19:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想做母親的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.81,0:19:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你自己誕下兒子吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機動堡壘，比基拿出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.09,0:19:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機械師離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.82,0:19:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.92,0:19:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在交戰中，請你戴上頭罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.49,0:19:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機師服已經阻住我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.89,0:19:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會受傷的，出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.20,0:19:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是露比.施羅的…布魯京？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.10,0:19:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,避開！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.32,0:19:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，細路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.72,0:20:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不用和無用的男人來往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.84,0:20:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，細路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.97,0:20:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不用和無用的男人來往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.01,0:20:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒艦隊沉沒了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.35,0:20:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是露比.施羅小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.83,0:20:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索.你沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.83,0:20:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.27,0:20:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍的機動戰士部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.31,0:20:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已趁機突破敵陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.01,0:20:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神聖軍事同盟的艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.61,0:20:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得到重整陣形的時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.71,0:20:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們稍為後退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.41,0:21:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.28,0:21:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比列騰死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.52,0:21:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何凱羅天使的\N格諾古不行動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.26,0:21:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐要來凱羅天使的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.82,0:21:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他正忙於奉承卡格持吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.39,0:21:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杜根艦隊也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.93,0:21:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先，\N我要了結一切，達斯羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.73,0:21:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是[斷頭台花娜]嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.24,0:21:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.49,0:21:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是能運用\N初次使用的東西嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.83,0:21:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來？  是鈴聲嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.23,0:21:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.33,0:21:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來和在\N卡沙尼里亞聼到的不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.37,0:21:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.51,0:22:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在銀色的海上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.58,0:22:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灼熱的波浪湧上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.45,0:22:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到跪下的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.05,0:22:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有變成說話，\N只是你的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.73,0:23:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能變得優美就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.00,0:23:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再次TENDERNESS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.87,0:23:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你的内心在月亮的菱鏡上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.84,0:23:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱着閃耀的未來在跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.51,0:23:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能再次和你見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.92,0:23:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你的瞳孔顯出孤獨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.86,0:23:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索面對忽視自己的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.70,0:23:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感到迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.67,0:23:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面，胡索和舒勒隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.71,0:23:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被鈴聲吸引飛往戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.27,0:23:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在達斯羅艦隊的攻擊之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.61,0:23:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色方舟漂流到\N凱羅天使那裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.81,0:23:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家不快點集合不行啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.88,0:23:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回，機動戰士V高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.62,0:23:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰場的彗星花娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.82,0:23:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請收看吧
